# Format:
#   roadmap <id> <status> "<name>"
#     track    <bootstrap|self-host|native|perf|ssot|ai-native|hybrid|cell|lora|ffi|...>
#     phase    <P0|P1|P7-6|...>
#     eta      <YYYY-MM-DD or TBD>
#     <key>    <value>
#
# status (locked, 5): live warn new deferred convention
# roadmap-status (locked, 5): planned active done blocked deferred
# required keys: track phase eta why
# standard keys (common): owner proof note depends-on unblocks

# ─── shared checkpoints (anima-mirror: dual_roadmap.json milestones) ───
# Cross-cutting milestones all tracks converge toward.
# Entries declare `reaches <CP>` to contribute, `requires <CP>` to gate.

